{"tid":1607363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如推一推前綫非勇武人人一個R95？","createTime":"2019-09-30T20:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T00:03:07.000Z","uid":295155,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"40fdbd9fe4f4103178342e61df0a6d43bd371253","tid":1607363,"uid":295155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rqyNfpd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrqyNfpd.png&h=0166fe00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1）平。平均$2x一個，棄裝都唔太心痛。<br />\n2）防護。有活性碳可防毒。<br />\n3）容易買。一般五金舖都有。<br />\n<br />\n唯一缺點不環保。大是大非面前，要保命無得選擇下，唯有在另一些地方做得環保一些將公保過。"},{"pid":"b2d85e9196336d5d2006ad1967591bbea5ca9ee3","tid":1607363,"uid":262263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:58:19.000Z","msg":"壽命？<br />\n<br />\n老老竇竇，好多人戴嘴企係前面食花生<br />\n好想搶走<br />\n<br />\n利申 睇直播見到<br />\n<br />\nbtw棄裝可揀啲位收埋，夜啲返去再執"},{"pid":"0c489c49161520853b0faab17ba42bed24812745","tid":1607363,"uid":215715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T21:55:07.000Z","msg":"p95幾錢個?"},{"pid":"de7b75a33cdb793cfe53537846893e69ae0df1d6","tid":1607363,"uid":225192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c489c49161520853b0faab17ba42bed24812745","tid":1607363,"uid":215715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T21:55:07.000Z","msg":"p95幾錢個?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:24:14.000Z","msg":"一個30 一盒廿個買計番28蚊個<br />\n如果五金冇賣油漆既地方會有<br />\n可以買黎派俾中後排市民"},{"pid":"11f4780f5db60f53904edc5c2ecc4ac337efc3c0","tid":1607363,"uid":195601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:34:52.000Z","msg":"r95 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\np95 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b9cafb933b920582f29d356dbcc47add1d6b68","tid":1607363,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:36:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">六區開花要對準政權，梗係去議員辦事處賀佢老母啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再</span></strong></span>企起街上面<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>圍警局</strong></span></span>，分區活動就應該<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>打游擊戰去搵該區既建制派議員</strong></span></span>同佢地開party一齊賀一賀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，至於邊一區去邊間就大家自己衡量下喇﹗<br />\n<br />\n屯門區區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=cef412ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n荃灣區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=3b3d3afe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n沙田區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=bd26ca00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n黃大仙區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%2599%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=391672bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n深水埗區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=c006e193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n灣仔區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=7ee7105b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話（呢個係每日都可以做既）</span></span></strong><br />\n打電話搵議員(之前有巴打post過出黎，可以自己搵下)問下國慶期間區內有咩最新活動、巴士路線、有咩醫生診所好介紹呀等等，電話打唔通既whatsapp都可以，無whatsapp既巴絲打可以send email去，連email都無既可以fax過去查詢下，無人應既話可以搵下無限fax大法fax到佢應機為止。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>2.連儂牆</strong></span></span><br />\n都係搵立法會議員/區議員辦事處啦，無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>3.裝修</strong></span></span><br />\n有好多議員都扎根起屋邨做左好耐，裡面啲裝修又殘又舊，有心既手足可以襯國慶幫佢地補下油、翻新下添置返少少國慶節日既氣氛，用咩色就自己決定啦。<br />\n補充:好多office既出入口好窄，大家入office查詢既時候動作唔好太大呀，唔小心撞到佢地d玻璃就大鑊喇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>4.餵office既龜龜食野(蟲系魔法師出動)</strong></span></span><br />\n巴絲打們都可以準備少少紅蟲、蚯蚓、生雞蛋、甜野呀個d比入面既龜龜食，可以吸引到更多蟲蟲輕易大量繁殖既就更好。大家知啦，議員們公事繁忙，萬一無時間餵佢地，龜龜都仲有少少野食丫嘛。<br />\n補充：拉開櫃桶餵既時候記住小心啲，唔好倒瀉手上罐可樂呀，會惹到成地蟻架！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>原post:</strong></span><br />\n國慶咁大件事 緊係要約埋建制議員賀佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605409</a>"},{"pid":"18235928ee9fe63208d245c58f74fb709581663c","tid":1607363,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:37:50.000Z","msg":"p95先得"},{"pid":"2051967936560bf07191cecc246209c7e358e8cb","tid":1607363,"uid":295155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2d85e9196336d5d2006ad1967591bbea5ca9ee3","tid":1607363,"uid":262263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T20:58:19.000Z","msg":"壽命？<br />\n<br />\n老老竇竇，好多人戴嘴企係前面食花生<br />\n好想搶走<br />\n<br />\n利申 睇直播見到<br />\n<br />\nbtw棄裝可揀啲位收埋，夜啲返去再執"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:57:31.000Z","msg":"壽命如果果日食過蛋，當然一次就棄喇～"},{"pid":"b70889e783878fcc1d210a62743c8ced36776225","tid":1607363,"uid":295155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de7b75a33cdb793cfe53537846893e69ae0df1d6","tid":1607363,"uid":225192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c489c49161520853b0faab17ba42bed24812745","tid":1607363,"uid":215715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T21:55:07.000Z","msg":"p95幾錢個?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:24:14.000Z","msg":"一個30 一盒廿個買計番28蚊個<br />\n如果五金冇賣油漆既地方會有<br />\n可以買黎派俾中後排市民"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T20:00:15.000Z","msg":"R95 散買都要廿幾蚊個wor～P95有咁平？邊度有？？介紹下。"},{"pid":"0ae86d1bf69fa0084a1e82619de3625fee64a6bb","tid":1607363,"uid":225192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b70889e783878fcc1d210a62743c8ced36776225","tid":1607363,"uid":295155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"